I dont record to my pc. I have reception problems so I have my radio 
hooked up to a set of computer speakers. I use a recorder which I set 
between the speakers I hold the radio in my hand have to move around 
to find a good spot which is something away from the speaker!!! So 
sometimes you can hear me,

Thanks for listening

Kay 


